# Security policies

This project takes security very seriously. If you find a security vulnerability, please report it at https://github.com/Itzdan0ul/dental-oe/issues.

## Security vulnerability reporting

When a security vulnerability is discovered, we will post a security announcement on our website and send an email to all our registered users. If you have reported a security vulnerability and wish to remain anonymous, please let us know at the time of reporting and we will do our best to respect your privacy.

## Known security vulnerabilities

- No known security vulnerabilities.

## Security tips for users

- Use strong and unique passwords for each account.
- Do not share your password with anyone.
- Keep your software and operating system up to date.
